{"article_id":"iAPKnhKNxpaIg33J","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Critics are slamming The New York Times ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"the newspaper has a \" hypocritical double standard \"","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"after the publication stood by its hiring of tech writer Sarah Jeong","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"despite several derogatory tweets of hers","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"aimed at white people .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Jeong tweeted","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that she gets joy out of being \" cruel to old white men , \" used a \" CancelWhitePeople \" hashtag","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and sent numerous other offensive tweets .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The tweets","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"- mostly from 2014 -","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"were unearthed earlier this week","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"after the Times announced","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Jeong was joining the paper .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The paper defended Jeong in a statement on Thursday ,","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"chalking her offensive comments up to a \" young Asian woman \"","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"\" imitating the rhetoric \" of her own online harassers .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Conservative columnist Daniella Greenbaum told","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that \" the issue at hand here is not about whether Jeong ' s tweets were racist or not.","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"\" Greenbaum says","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that hypocrisy is the real issue .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"\" Jeong claimed","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"she was kidding .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Good enough ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"I guess ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"although swap the word ' white '","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and insert black , Mexican , or Jewish in any of her tweets","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and I have a feeling","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"we ' d be having a very different conversation , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Greenbaum said .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"Much like Jeong , Greenbaum is a young columnist","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"who has garnered a lot of attention .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"But Greenbaum is a staunch conservative ,","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"who last month resigned from her job as a columnist at Business Insider","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"after the website removed an already-published piece","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"defending Scarlett Johansson","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"for signing on to play a transgender man .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"The piece apparently offended some of her liberal colleagues","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"and Greenbaum walked away from her job","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"after being censored .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Johansson later backed away from the role .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"Greenbaum ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"who didn ' t exactly receive overwhelming support during her own ordeal ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"noticed","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that many in the media industry have rushed to defend Jeong .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"\" The New York Times , and much of the media chose to believe","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"that she was kidding ,","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"or to posit","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"even if she wasn ' t kidding ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"her misguided beliefs are not reason enough","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"to fire her .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"In other words , they extended her a brand of courtesy","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"never offered to people","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"who are right of center , \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Greenbaum said .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"\" That ' s the issue here . \"","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"High-powered liberal media members such as HuffPost Editor-in-Chief Lydia Polgreen and leadership at The Verge ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"where Jeong currently works ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"have defended her rhetoric .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"The former Business Insider columnist said","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"we have \" created an enormous , hypocritical double standard","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that is entirely unjust \"","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"when it comes to judgment in the media industry .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"\" Let ' s see how Jeong reacts next time","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"a conservative finds themselves in a similar situation .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Something tells me","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"she won ' t speak out on their behalf , \"","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Greenbaum said .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"Media Research Center analyst Kristine Marsh wrote ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" The New York Times justified her racist tweets , \"","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"and called the paper ' s statement laughable .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Some social media users agreed","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"and blasted the paper 's decision on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"The New York Times doubled-down on Jeong ' s behalf in their statement","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"announcing support for the tech writer .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"The newspaper stated :","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"\" We hired Sarah Jeong","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"because of the exceptional work","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"she has done ...","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"her journalism and the fact","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"that she is a young Asian woman","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"have made her a subject of frequent online harassment .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"For a period of time she responded to that harassment","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"by imitating the rhetoric of her harassers . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":169,"left":114,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":98,"right":113,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{